{"tid":2415594,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"Now新聞台: 約20宗初步確診","createTime":"2021-02-20T11:15:16.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-20T13:23:45.000Z","uid":5195,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"a228b618b1556993c9bac14f615d6ab75c23210a","tid":2415594,"uid":5195,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-20T11:15:16.000Z","msg":"【Now新聞台】本港新增15宗新冠病毒確診個案，10宗屬本地感染，當中4宗源頭不明，另外有約20宗初步確診。<br />\n<br />\n源頭不明個案中，42歲西醫林嘉揚確診，診所位於葵涌和宜商場仁心醫務中心，傳染期曾在診所工作，本周四最後一天上班，診所須關閉14日。一名70歲女士亦確診，住在火炭銀禧花園6座，大廈需要強制檢測；一名主要在東涌交更的的士司機確診。<br />\n<br />\n另外，有六宗確診與早前個案有關聯，包括港台一名24歲男助理編導，他曾短暫逗留化妝間，提取外景服裝，與早前確診髮型師無接觸。港台電視大廈將被納入強制檢測公告，流動檢測車停泊港台，供員工做檢測。"},{"pid":"3738c5b513a1d2b65da57e7c825bcbedfa194172","tid":2415594,"uid":5195,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-20T11:16:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FpiD98AB.jpg&amp;h=8f803e25&amp;s=540\" />"},{"pid":"359c6d1de3eba57f00796a372f213d6c4c9cc2ba","tid":2415594,"uid":321012,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-20T11:16:56.000Z","msg":"快升<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d87ef673ae7a1dd575dd1a4a4cf81fd86d9c2db9","tid":2415594,"uid":76804,"like":14,"dislike":4,"score":10,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-20T11:30:34.000Z","msg":"想唔想第五波<br />\n想 可以wfh或者彈性上班時間 經濟攬炒 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n唔想 我要睇戲出街食飯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1d4f80e0e2bd0fb978e40aee0b23a22b3ced6969","tid":2415594,"uid":5195,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-20T11:42:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/gun.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9b5acc34ab78ee10e42dc41cb847b63baf7ce48a","tid":2415594,"uid":11809,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"re